1 - Create Component in Angular : 

ng g c products/product-detail --Flat(It is not created folder)


2 - Create guard in Angular : 

ng g g products/product-detail


3 - Create module in Angular : 

ng g m products/product --flat -m app (- m app, we put its finctonality in app module.)


4 - Install Angular CLI - 

npm install -g @angular/cli

5 - Show Version :

ng v


6 - Cli createng new project:(ng new) 

ng new 'project Name'


7 - Cli launches server :(ng serve)

ng serve (It's not open default browser)

ng serve -o (It's open default browser)

8 - CLI generate command :(ng g) : get list (ng g --help)

generate Component : ng g c component-name (ng g c welcome)
generate module : ng g m module-name
generate dataService: ng g s service-name

and so on

9 - CLI Test command : 
	(ng test) (Run unit test using Karma)
		ng test (Its run on karma tool)

	(ng e2e) (end to end Test using Protractor)
		ng e2e (Its open browser and close browser)

10 - Help Command :

ng help

11 - We can add third party components

ng add ngx-bootstrap  --component buttons
ng add ngx-bootstrap  --component datepicker
ng add ngx-bootstrap  --component timepicker
ng add ngx-bootstrap  --component rating



